# NEHotspotHelperConfidence.low

**Case**

The helper has some confidence in being able to handle the network.

## Declaration

```swift
case low
```

## Confidence Levels

- **NEHotspotHelperConfidence.high**: The helper has high confidence in being able to handle the network.
- **NEHotspotHelperConfidence.none**: The helper is unable to handle the network.
